def clean_text(text):
    # decode url
    text = urllib.parse.unquote_plus(text)
    # remove html tags
    text = re.sub('<[^<]+?>', '', text)
    # remove multiple spaces + "\r" + "\n" + "\t"
    text = " ".join(text.split())
    return text
